an%20be%20a%20day%20trip.%20In%20Houston%2C%20going%20to%20Galveston%2C%20which%20is%20about%2050%20miles%20away%2C%20wasn't%20worth%20it%20unless%20we%20stayed%20for%20a%20weekend.%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20ski%20the%20mountains%20in%20Oregon%2C%20but%20I%20could%20at%20least%20visit%20and%20snowshoe%20there.%20There%20aren't%20any%20mountains%20like%20that%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20Houston's%20arboretum%20and%20city%20gardens%20in%20our%20free%20time%2C%20but%20they%20were%20paved%2C%20crowded%2C%20and%20hot.%20Even%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Portland%2C%20hikers%20can%20get%20lost%20alone%20in%20muddy%20forests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daily%20Houston%20commute%2C%20which%20could%20take%20me%20anywhere%20from%20one%20to%20three%20hours%20a%20day%20depending%20on%20my%20schedule%2C%20exhausted%20me.%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20choosing%20a%20central%20location%20when%20I%20chose%20our%20apartment%2C%20but%20the%20scale%20of%20Houston%20was%20greater%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHousing%20is%20more%20expensive%20in%20Portland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20planning%20the%20move%2C%20I%20kept%20my%20housing%20budget%20between%20%241%2C100%20and%20%241%2C200%20for%20a%20one-bedroom%20to%20abate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flifestyle-creep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifestyle%20creep%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20save%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Portland%2C%20our%20rent%20was%20moving%20closer%20to%20%241%2C400%20for%20smaller%20and%20smaller%20apartments%2C%20but%20I%20found%20a%20place%20in%20Houston%20on%20the%20cheaper%20end%20of%20my%20budget%20that%20offered%20more%20square%20footage%2C%20a%20saltwater%20pool%2C%20a%20gym%2C%20and%20gated%20parking.%20I'd%20only%20had%20street%20parking%20in%20Portland%2C%20and%20apartments%20with%20garages%20charged%20between%20%24100%20and%20%24%20200%20a%20month%20for%20one%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%