0he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%2055-year-old%2C%20the%20GPS%20route%20took%20him%20from%20Nyanga%2C%20which%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20the%20greatest%26quot%3B%20and%20traffic%20got%20so%20cluttered%20that%20he%20had%20to%20come%20to%20a%20stop.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20he%20said%20that%20four%20men%20circled%20his%20car%20before%20shooting%20him%20in%20the%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20got%20slow%20enough%20so%20that%20it%20was%20stopped%2C%20(and)%20the%20guy%20reached%20in%2C%20opened-%20hit%20the%20lock%2C%20opened%20the%20door%2C%20(and%20on%20of)%20his%20accomplice(s)%20opened%20the%20passenger%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fischel%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20tourist%20said%20he%20tried%20to%20reach%20for%20the%20man's%20gun%20but%20the%20shooter%20%26quot%3Bswung%20away%20from%20(me)%20while%20his%20accomplice%20grabbed%20some%20of%20the%20goods%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20car.%20He%20was%20then%20shot%20and%20the%20men%20grabbed%20the%20keys%20and%20kicked%20him%20out%20of%20his%20vehicle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20I%20opened%20the%20boot%20to%20try%20to%20grab%20my%20bag%2C%20which%20I%20did%2C%20and%20then%20they%20chased%20me%20down%20and%20grabbed%2C%20took%20the%20bag%20from%20me%2C%20and%20left%20me%20there%20with%20a%20bullet%20wound%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fischel%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20spit%20out%20a%20couple%20of%20teeth%20and%20the%20bullet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fitalian-man-who-killed-girlfriend-over-breadcrumbs-released-due-to-prisons-poor-diet-4572387%5C%22%3EItalian%20Man%20Who%20Killed%20Girlfriend%20Over%20Breadcrumbs%20Released%20Due%20To%20Prison's%20Poor%20Diet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Mr%20Fischel%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20local%20hospital%20whe