ll%20slip%20into%20recession%20next%20year%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that'll%20lead%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20bringing%20in%20steep%20interest-rate%20cuts%2C%20according%20to%20one%20top%20European%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20said%20Tuesday%20that%20it's%20expecting%20the%20Fed%20to%20respond%20to%20falling%20inflation%20and%20an%20economic%20slump%20by%20slashing%20rates%20by%20an%20eye-popping%20275%20basis%20points%20%E2%80%93%20nearly%20four%20times%20the%2075-basis-point%20reduction%20the%20market%20is%20currently%20expecting%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmegroup.com%2Fmarkets%2Finterest-rates%2Fcme-fedwatch-tool.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECME%20Group's%20Fedwatch%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20key%20features%20of%20UBS's%20forecast%20is%20the%20very%20pronounced%20Fed%20easing%20cycle%20seen%20unfolding%20from%20March%202024%20onwards%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20team%20led%20by%20economist%20Arend%20Kapteyn%20and%20strategist%20Bhanu%20Baweja%20said%20in%20a%20research%20note%20published%20Tuesday%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20expect%20rates%20to%20plunge%20to%20just%201.25%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed's%20cuts%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20response%20to%20the%20forecasted%20US%20recession%20in%20Q2-Q3%202024%20and%20the%20ongoing%20slowdown%20in%20both%20headline%20and%20core%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20March%202022%2C%20the%20Fed%20has%20lifted%20borrowing%20costs%20from%20near-zero%20to%20around%205.5%25%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20soaring%20prices.%20Inflation%20hit%20a%20four-decade%20high%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-cpi-price-growth-june-2022-7%5C%22%3E9.1%25%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20but%20has%20since%20started%20to%20cool%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0although%20it's%20still%20running%20way%20clear%20of%20the%20central%20bank's%202%25%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20tightening%20campaign%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20weigh%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20but%20the%20US%20has%20avoided%20a%20recession%20so%20far.%20The%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgdp-recession-outlook-economy-gross-domestic-product-third-quarter-2023-10%5C%22%3Egross%20domestic%20product%20expanded%204.9%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20for%20its%20highest%20growth%20rate%20in%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20jobs%20market%20has%20also%20held%20up%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Fed's%20interest-rate%20hikes%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-unemployment-rate-recession-outlook-labor-market-wages-federal-reserve-2023-11%5C%22%3Eunemployment%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20creeping%20up%20in%20recent%20months%20but%20still%20hovering%20below%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recession%20prediction%20laid%20out%20by%20Kapteyn%20and%20Baweja%20appears%20to%20clash%20with%20a%20separate%20outlook%20shared%20by%20UBS's%20head%20of%20asset%20allocation%20for%20the%20Americas%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Draho%20said%20in%20a%20presentation%20that%20the%20US%20economy's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-today-job-market-recession-outlook-economic-news-2023-7%5C%22%3Esurprising%20resilience%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20has%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-boom-high-growth-inflation-interest-rates-stocks-bonds-ubs-2023-11%5C%22%3Eroaring%20'20s%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20period%20defined%20by%20higher%20GDP%20growth%2C%20inflation%2C%20bond%20yields%2C%20and%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-2024-recession-fed-interest-rate-cuts-ubs-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C