y%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20The%20film%2C%20which%20is%20the%20third%20installment%20of%20the%20successful%20Tiger%20franchise%2C%20recorded%20the%20highest-grossing%20Monday%20for%20a%20Hindi%20film%20in%20Indian%20cinema%20history.%20Trade%20analyst%20Girish%20Wankhede%20attributes%20the%20film's%20success%20to%20its%20strong%20franchise%20power%20and%20the%20excitement%20surrounding%20Yash%20Raj's%20spy%20universe.%20The%20calculated%20release%20date%20during%20the%20festive%20season%20also%20contributed%20to%20its%20traction.%20Wankhede%20predicts%20a%20long%20and%20successful%20run%20for%20Tiger%203%20at%20the%20box%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Vaibhavi%20V%20Risbood%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inflation%20Drops%3A%20BJP%20Governments%20Outpace%20Rivals%20Among%20Poll-Bound%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20advanced%20economies%20have%20been%20grappling%20with%20elevated%20prices%20for%20months%2C%20consumer%20price%20inflation%20in%20India%20dropped%20to%20a%20five-month%20low%20in%20October.%20Apart%20from%20prices%20of%20cereals%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20pulses%2C%20the%20changes%20in%20most%20other%20items%20in%20October%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20month%20last%20year%20were%20relatively%20subdued.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20two%20items%20that%20had%20previously%20driven%20consumer%20prices%20up%2C%20edible%20oil%20and%20fuel%2C%20became%20cheaper%20last%20month%2C%20according%20to%20the%20recently%20released%20government%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20key%20highlights%20of%20the%20data%20released%20on%20Monday%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmong%20the%20larger%20states%2C%20consumer%20price%20inflation%20was%20higher%20in%20nine%20states%2C%20with%20Odisha%20reporting%20the%20highest%20rate%20at%206.47%20per%20cent.%20Of%20these%20nine%20states%2C%20three%20are%20governed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Telangana%20are%20among%20states%20with%20inflation%20rates%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20consumer%20price%20inflation%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20seven%20states%20reported%20figures%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average.%20Two%20of%20these%20states%20are%20under%20BJP%20rule%2C%20as%20per%20data%20released%20by%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO)%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation.%20Bihar%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20are%20among%20states%20with%20higher%20rural%20inflation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20inflation%20rates%20are%20among%20the%20lowest%2C%20at%20four%20per%20cent%20or%20below.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%20prices%20of%20fuel%20and%20light%20and%20edible%20oils%20dropped%20in%20October%2C%20there%20was%20a%20marginal%20increase%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20vegetables%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20transport%20and%20communications.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20The%20Economist%20published%20an%20article%20analyzing%20the%20inflation%20trend%20in%20developed%20countries.%20Their%20analysis%20indicates%20that%20inflation%20remains%20quite%20entrenched%2C%20even%20more%20so%20now%20than%20in%202022.%20The%20journal%20concludes%20that%20the%20situation%20continues%20to%20be%20challenging%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20with%20some%20improvement%20seen%20in%20Italy%2C%20Spain%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20South%20Korea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20India%20emerging%20as%20one%20of%20the%20bright%20spots%2C%20given%20the%20situation%20worldwide%3F%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20investment%20bank%20major%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20recently%20upgraded%20India's%20markets%20to%20overweight%20in%20an%20otherwise%20tricky%20period%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region.%20This%20follows%20earlier%20upgrades%20from%20institutions%20such%20as%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20CLSA%2C%20and%20Nomura.%20The%20factors%20driving%20these%20upgrades%20include%20macroeconomic%20stability%20in%20India%2C%20with%20a%20subdued%20inflation%20trajectory%20being%20one%20of%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699954980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F5vjmr3qo_inflation_625x300_12_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finflation-drops-bjp-governments-outpace-rivals-among-poll-bound-states-4572967%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20many%20advanced%20economies%20have%20been%20grappling%20with%20elevated%20prices%20for%20months%2C%20consumer%20price%20inflation%20in%20India%20dropped%20to%20a%20five-month%20low%20in%20October.%20Apart%20from%20prices%20of%20cereals%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20pulses%2C%20the%20changes%20in%20most%20other%20items%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finflation-drops-bjp-governments-outpace-rivals-among-poll-bound-states-4572967%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finflation-drops-bjp-governments-outpace-rivals-among-poll-bound-states-4572967%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finflation-drops-bjp-governments-outpace-rivals-among-poll-bound-states-4572967%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dogbite%20Victims%20To%20Get%2010%2C000%20For%20%26quot%3BEach%20Teeth%20Mark%26quot%3B%3A%20Big%20High%20Court%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20judgment%20likely%20to%20set%20a%20precedent%20and%20spark%20a%20huge%20debate%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20the%20State%20shall%20be%20%26quot%3Bprimarily%20responsible%26quot%3B%20to%20pay%20compensation%20in%20cases%20of%20attacks%20by%20stray%20animals%20such%20as%20dogs%20and%20cattle.%20In%20dog%20bite%20cases%2C%20it%20has%20said%2C%20the%20assistance%20shall%20be%20a%20minimum%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20%26quot%3Bper%20teeth%20mark%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20minimum%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20per%200.2%20cm%20of%20wound%20where%20the%20flesh%20has%20come%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20bunch%20of%20193%20petitions%20relating%20to%20attacks%20by%20stray%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20comes%20amid%20a%20huge%20debate%20in%20the%20country%20on%20the%20stray%20dog%20menace.%20The%20death%20of%2049-year-old%20Parag%20Desai%2C%20executive%20director%20with%20Wagh%20Bakri%20Tea%20Group%2C%20in%20October%20had%20sparked%20off%20a%20fresh%20round%20in%20the%20debate.%20A%20hospital%20statement%20had%20said%20Mr%20Desai%20died%20of%20a%20haemorrhage%20suffered%20in%20a%20fall%20after%20stray%20dogs%20chased%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20tragic%20incident%2C%20a%20section%20of%20social%20media%20users%20demanded%20urgent%20steps%20to%20tackle%20the%20stray%20dog%20problem%2C%20pointing%20to%20multiple%20cases%20of%20deaths%20and%20injuries%2C%20including%20to%20children%2C%20in%20animal%20attacks.%20Growing%20public%20anger%20over%20such%20cases%20has%20also%20led%20to%20incidents%20of%20animal%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20State%20shall%20be%20primarily%20responsible%20to%20pay%20compensation%20with%C2%A0a%20right%20to%20recover%20the%20same%20from%20the%20defaulting%20Agencies%2F%20Instrumentalities%20of%20the%20State%20and%2For%20the%20private%20person%2C%20if%20any%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Court%20said%20in%20its%20order%20on%20a%20petition%20seeking%20compensation%20in%20a%20dogbite%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20also%20asked%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20and%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Chandigarh%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20that%20will%20decide%20on%20compensation%20to%20be%20paid%20in%20cases%20of%20accidents%20caused%20or%20attacks%20by%20stray%20animals.%20These%20include%20animals%20such%20as%20cows%2C%20bulls%2C%20oxen%2C%20donkeys%2C%20dogs%2C%20nilgai%2C%20buffaloes%2C%20and%20wild%2C%20pet%20and%20deserted%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20said%20Committee%20shall%20be%20comprised%20of%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20concerned%20District%20as%20its%20Chairperson%20and%20shall%20have%20the%20following%20member%20(a)%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2FDeputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Traffic)%2C%20(b)%20Sub%20Divisional%20Magistrate%20of%20the%20concerned%20area%2C%20(c)%20The%20District%20Transport%20Officer%2C%20(d)%20Representative%20of%20the%20Chief%20Medical%20Officer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judgment%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20is%20crucial%20considering%20the%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20the%20stray%20dog%20menace%2C%20an%20immensely%20polarising%20subject%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%202001%2C%20municipal%20authorities%20could%20euthanise%20stray%20dogs%20to%20keep%20public%20places%20safe.%20In%202001%20came%20the%20Animal%20Birth%20Control%20(Dogs)%20Rules.%20These%20rules%20created%20a%20separate%20category%20called%20%26quot%3Bstreet%20dogs%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20they%20should%20be%20sterilised%20and%20immunised%20by%20%26quot%3Bparticipation%20of%20animal%20welfare%20organizations%2C%20private%20individuals%20and%20the%20local%20authority%26quot%3B.%20Lack%20of%20adequate%20funds%20and%20manpower%20have%20frequently%20stalled%20such%20exercises%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20spike%20in%20stray%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202001%20rules%20were%20silent%20on%20euthanising%20stray%20dogs%20except%20those%20%26quot%3Bincurably%20ill%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bmortally%20wounded%26quot%3B.%20They%20also%20said%20dogs%20caught%20for%20sterlisation%20and%20vaccination%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Breleased%20in%20the%20same%20area%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publi