3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThirty-one%20percent%20of%20those%20surveyed%20said%20they%20currently%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-your-employer-doesnt-care-about-you-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboss%20who%20exhibits%20toxic%20behavior%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%2071%25%20said%20they%20have%20had%20at%20least%20one%20toxic%20boss%20throughout%20their%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20nothing%20short%20of%20astonishing%20how%20the%20presence%20of%20toxicity%20not%20only%20persists%20but%20actively%20flourishes%20within%20certain%20workplace%20environments%2C%26quot%3B%20Libby%20Rodney%2C%20the%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20The%20Harris%20Poll%2C%20told%20Insider%20over%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20toxicity%20can%20lead%20to%20to%20mental%20health%20problems%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20why%20so%20many%20workers%20seek%20therapy%3A%2074%25%20of%20workers%20who%20said%20they%20have%20a%20toxic%20boss%20reported%20feeling%20anxiety%20over%20the%20weekend%20when%20thinking%20about%20returning%20to%20work%20on%20Monday%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-week-sunday-scaries-decrease-improved-work-life-balance-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%26quot%3BSunday%20scaries%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20while%2053%25%20reported%20having%20nightmares%20about%20their%20bosses.%20Thirty-four%20percent%20of%20those%20with%20toxic%20bosses%20reported%20engaging%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-executives-report-heavy-alcohol-drinking-painkillers-substance-use-stress-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoping%20mechanisms%20like%20drinking%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20overeating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20toll%20toxic%20bosses%20can%20take%20on%20workers'%20lives%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20workers%20with%20toxic%20bosses%20say%20they%20tolerate%20them%20for%20financial%20reasons%2C%20includi