ris%20Poll%20survey%20found.%20If%20their%20bosses%20were%20to%20nurture%20a%20positive%20work%20environment%2C%20those%20workers%20said%20they%20would%20put%20extra%20effort%20into%20their%20jobs%20and%20be%20willing%20to%20take%20on%20more%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20not%2C%20workers%20may%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-loud-quitting-job-definition-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecide%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20who've%20been%20dealing%20with%20a%20bad%20work%20environment%2C%20this%20will%20become%20a%20critical%20time%20to%20decide%20if%20they%20still%20want%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Rodney%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-seek-therapy-toxic-bosses-mental-health-anxiety-study-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699953541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65525ece36d588dc55cf5d6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-seek-therapy-toxic-bosses-mental-health-anxiety-study-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2271%25%20of%20US%20workers%20reported%20having%20at%20least%20one%20toxic%20boss%20throughout%20their%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22amok%40insider.com%20(Aaron%20Mok)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-seek-therapy-toxic-bosses-mental-health-anxiety-study-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Xi%20Jinping%20looks%20to%20steady%20ties%20at%20Apec%20meeting%20with%20Joe%20Biden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699953477000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105206629%2Cimgsize-681001.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatim