0are%20part%20of%20Operation%201107%2C%20launched%20jointly%20by%20all%20the%20resistance%20forces%20against%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20military%20dictatorship%20since%20October%2027.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20of%20the%20fierce%20fighting%20%E2%80%93%20involving%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20aerial%20attacks%20%E2%80%93%20hundreds%20of%20people%20have%20fled%20home%20to%20safety.%20The%20entry%20of%20fresh%20groups%20of%20refugees%20into%20the%20border%20town%20of%20Zokhawthar%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Champai%20district%20this%20November%2012%20is%20a%20fallout%20of%20these%20combats.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbattle-close-to-india-border-forces-1400-into-mizoram-one-dead%2Farticle67528563.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20one%20Myanmarese%20citizen%20had%20lost%20his%20life%20from%20shrapnel%20injury%20soon%20after%20entering%20the%20Indian%20side%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.themizorampost.net%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMizoram%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%2017%20others%20have%20been%20injured%20too%20in%20the%20exchange%20of%20fire%20between%20the%20Myanmar%20army%20and%20the%20resistance%20forces%2C%20which%20includes%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20wounded%20have%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20District%20Hospital%20in%20Champai%20for%20more%20extensive%20medical%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20The%20Mizoram%20Post.%20The%20news%20report%20said%20the%20Young%20Mizo%20Association%20had%20stepped%20in%20to%20provide%20food%20to%20the%20affected%20lot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeputy%20commissioner%20of%20Champai%2C%20James%20Lalrinchhana%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20there%20were%20reports%20of%20bombing%20(by%20the%20Myanmar%20army)%20near%20the%20international%20border%2C%20there%20was%20no%20damage%20on%20the%20Indian%20side.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20quoted%20him%20on%20November%2013%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CEfforts%20are%20underway%20to%20confirm%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20with%20a%20team%20of%20magistrates%20dispatched%20to%20Zokhawthar.%E2%80%9D%20Zokhawthar%20is%20about%20205%20km%20from%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Aizawl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECalling%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20refuges%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Crecurring%20pattern%20for%20over%20two%20years%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20said%20they%20%E2%80%9Coften%20return%20when%20the%20situation%20stabilizes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20The%20Hindu%20quoted%20L.%20Hruaimawia%2C%20the%20liaison%20officer%20of%20the%20district%20level%20committee%20on%20Myanmar%20refugees%2C%20saying%20the%20current%20number%20of%20refuges%20stand%20at%20%E2%80%9Cabout%201400%E2%80%9D%2C%20The%20Mizoram%20Post%20said%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cover%201000%E2%80%9D.%20In%20total%2C%20the%20liaison%20officer%20said%2C%205%2C604%20refugees%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20Zokhawthar%2C%20located%20about%2042%20kms%20from%20the%20district%20headquarters%2C%20Champai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20refugees%20from%20the%20Chin%20state%20share%20kinship%20with%20the%20Mizos%20and%20Kukis%20in%20Manipur.%20With%20the%202021%20military%20coup%20in%20Myanmar%20leading%20to%20armed%20resistance%20movements%2C%20thousands%20of%20people%20including%20former%20parliamentarians%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699951505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14134513%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-1.30.51.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmyanmar-mizoram-refugees-junta%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20days%20of%20combat%20between%20the%20Tatmadaw%20and%20the%20Chin%20National%20Army%2C%20the%20former's%20base%2C%20Reh%20Khaw%20Da%20in%20Falam%20township%2C%20has%20fallen%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20pro-democracy%20forces%2C%20reports%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmyanmar-mizoram-refugees-junta%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20BJP%2C%20Congress%20Spar%20Over%20%26quot%3BFake%26quot%3B%20Video%20Of%20Minister's%20Son%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20on%20the%20defensive%20in%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20after%20a%20video%20that%20seems%20to%20show%20Union%20Agriculture%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnarendra-singh-tomar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Singh%20Tomar%3C%2Fa%3E's%20son%20negotiating%20a%20'deal'%20worth%20Rs%20500%20crore%20surfaced%20Monday.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20video%20this%20month%3B%20last%20week%20a%20video%20seemed%20to%20show%20Devendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20-%20whose%20father%20is%20among%20the%20big-names%20fielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20for%20Friday's%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Felections%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_mainnavgation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelection%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0-%20discussing%20three%20deals%20worth%20a%20combined%20Rs%20139%20crore.%C2%A0Asked%20about%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20Tomar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20not%20waste%20time%20on%20fakes...%26quot%3B.%20The%20BJP%20has%20dismissed%20the%20videos%2C%20which%20the%20Congress%20has%20slammed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20state%20boss%2C%20VD%20Sharma%2C%20has%20called%20the%20video%20%26quot%3Bfake'%20and%20accused%20the%20opposition%20party%2C%20lacking%20any%20real%20issue%20to%20raise%2C%20of%20releasing%20the%20clips%20to%20unsettle%20voters%20ahead%20of%20polling%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20complaint%20has%20been%20made%20and