C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20focus%20our%20resources%20even%20more%20on%20the%20areas%20that%20are%20growing%20with%20the%20highest%20potential%20to%20drive%20our%20business%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Christoph%20Hartmann%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20Amazon%20Games%2C%20in%20the%20Nov.%2013%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20began%20informing%20employees%20Monday%20morning%20that%20their%20roles%20had%20been%20eliminated%2C%20in%20the%20second%20cut%20to%20the%20division%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20last%20week%20also%20began%20cutting%20jobs%20in%20its%20streaming%20music%20and%20podcast%20division%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%20It%20also%20cut%20a%20very%20small%20number%20of%20jobs%20in%20its%20human%20resources%20unit%20known%20as%20People%20Experience%20and%20Technology%2C%20or%20PXT%2C%20the%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20games%20division%20offers%20downloadable%20versions%20of%20many%20video%20games%2C%20on%20a%20monthly%20rotation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20Twitch%20channels%20and%20other%20services.%20The%20company%20remains%20focused%20on%20developing%20and%20publishing%20games%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BBlue%20Protocol%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20free%20games%20offered%20within%20Prime%20Gaming%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Gaming%20is%20a%20perk%20offered%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%24139%20annual%20Prime%20membership%20that%20includes%20free%20shipping%20and%20free%20streaming%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20listened%20to%20our%20customers%20and%20we%20know%20delivering%20free%20games%20every%20month%20is%20what%20they%20want%20most%2C%20so%20we%20are%20refining%20our%20Prime%20benefit%20to%20increase%20our%20focus%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Hartmann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Amazon%20cut%20about%20100%20jobs%20in%20the%20games%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20third-quarter%20net%20income%20far%20surpassed%20analysts'%20es