taka%20Bans%20Head%20Cover%20In%20Recruitment%20Exams%2C%20Allows%20Mangalasutra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20Examination%20Authority%20(KEA)%20restricted%20all%20forms%20of%20head%20cover%20in%20the%20exam%20hall%20during%20recruitment%20exams%20for%20various%20boards%20and%20corporations%20to%20avoid%20malpractice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20dress%20code%20does%20not%20explicitly%20ban%20hijab%2C%20it%20is%20implied%20by%20the%20new%20guidelines.%20The%20order%20said%20that%20this%20is%20part%20of%20the%20effort%20to%20stop%20exam%20malpractices%20using%20Bluetooth%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20November%206%2C%20a%20woman%20appearing%20for%20the%20Karnataka%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20examination%20was%20asked%20to%20remove%20her%20'mangalsutra'%20before%20entering%20the%20exam%20hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20protests%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%2C%20the%20KEA%20has%20now%20allowed%20women%20to%20wear%20mangalasutra%20and%20toe%20rings%20in%20the%20examination%20hall%20while%20restricting%20other%20jewellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recruitment%20exams%20of%20various%20boards%20and%20corporations%20are%20to%20be%20held%20on%20November%2018%20and%2019%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20October%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20had%20allowed%20students%20to%20wear%20the%20Hijab%2C%20during%20competitive%20exams.%20The%20Higher%20Education%20Minister%20MC%20Sudhakar%20had%20allowed%20aspirants%20to%20come%20to%20examination%20centres%20wearing%20the%20Hijab%20sparking%20off%20protests%20by%20right-wing%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20complaints%20of%20usage%20of%20Bluetooth%20devices%20by%20certain%20students%20the%20state%20government%20this%20time%20decided%20to%20enforce%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20government%20had%20on%20November%2011%20ordered%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20state%20CID%20into%20an%20incident%20where%20candidates%20at%20Kalaburagi%20and%