was%20co-created%20by%20journalist%20Issacharoff%20and%20lead%20actor%20Lior%20Raz%2C%20based%20on%20their%20experiences%20in%20the%20Mista'arvim%20counterterrorism%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20all%20the%20respect%20due%20to%20our%20TV%20show%2C%20we're%20not%20even%20close%20to%20reality%20because%20reality%20is%20way%20more%20complicated%20than%20everything%20we%20have%20written%2C%26quot%3B%20Issacharoff%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20the%20morning%20when%20Hamas%20militants%2C%20under%20cover%20of%20a%20rocket%20barrage%2C%20broke%20through%20the%20militarised%20Gaza%20border%20and%20launched%20their%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel%20that%20officials%20say%20claimed%20around%201%2C200%20lives%20and%20saw%20240%20hostages%20taken%20back%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surprise%20onslaught%20sparked%20an%20intense%20retaliatory%20campaign%20of%20air%20strikes%20and%20a%20ground%20invasion%20that%20have%20claimed%20more%20than%2011%2C240%20lives%2C%20according%20to%20Hamas%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20concern%20has%20flared%20over%20the%20high%20death%20toll%20among%20Palestinian%20civilians%2C%20many%20of%20them%20children%2C%20as%20fierce%20combat%20rages%20around%20embattled%20Gaza%20City%20hospitals%2C%20and%20regional%20tensions%20boil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Not%20Fauda%2C'real%20life'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssacharoff%20remembered%20the%20day%20it%20all%20started%20and%20missile%20alarm%20sirens%20blared%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20behave%20like%20the%20creator%20of%20the%20show%2C%20or%20a%20journalist%20--%20at%20that%20time%20I%20am%20just%20a%20human%20being.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20the%20(news%20of)%20atrocities%20coming%20from%20the%20south%2C%20first%20dozens%20of%20people%20killed%2C%20then%20it's%20hundreds%2C%20you%20realise%20it's%20the%20biggest%20number%20of%20Jews%20killed%20in%20one%20day%20since%20the%20Holocaust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20after%20the%20attacks%2C%20Issacharoff%20said%20he%20and%20Raz%2C%20who%20plays%20the%20unit's%20main%20character%20Doron%2C%20rushed%20to%20the%20Hamas-hit%20southern%20city%20of%20Sderot%20to%20help%20evacuate%20survivors%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20the%20fire%20zone%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20had%20also%20volunteered%20with%20the%20group%20Brothers%20in%20Arms%2C%20which%20before%20the%20war%20had%20protested%20against%20right-wing%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20and%20which%20now%20helps%20affected%20communities%20in%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2012%2C%20amid%20a%20call-up%20of%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20reservists%2C%20another%20series%20actor%2C%20Idan%20Amedi%2C%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20in%20military%20fatigues%20and%20the%20message%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20a%20scene%20from%20Fauda%2C%20it's%20real%20life%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssacharoff%20bemoaned%20his%20dead%20production%20team%20member%20Meir%20as%20someone%20who%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20positive%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Balways%20ready%20to%20help%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20undercover%20operator%20pointed%20to%20the%20hell%20of%20urban%20combat%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%2024%2F7%20threat%20of%20getting%20killed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20fight%20in%20an%20open-air%20urban%20area%2C%20the%20threat%20can%20come%20from%20a%20window%2C%20from%20a%20door%2C%20from%20a%20tunnel%2C%20from%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20that%20most%20of%20the%20time%20the%20enemy%20is%20not%20wearing%20uniforms.%20They%20can%20look%20like%20me.%20But%20when%20they%20take%20the%20AK-47%20and%20shoot%20you%2C%20that's%20the%20only%20thing%20--%20that%20you%20cannot%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20an%20enemy%20and%20a%20civilian.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20No%20'good%20explanation'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20season%20of%20Fauda%20was%20set%20inside%20a%20fictional%20Gaza%20and%20centred%20on%20a%20hostage%20rescue%20operation%20by%20the%20unit%20whose%20members%20speak%20Arabic%20and%20wear%20disguise%20to%20assimilate%20among%20local%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssacharoff%20again%20stressed%20the%20chasm%20between%20a%20TV%20show%20and%20the%20worst%20war%20yet%20in%20the%20decades-old%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20undercover%20agents%20are%20more%20for%20times%20of%20no%20war%2C%20times%20of%20tension.%20They%20need%20to%20work%20very%20secretly%2C%20very%20hush-hush%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20there%20is%20a%20war%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20undercover%20teams.%20You%20need%20a%20full%20division%20of%20tanks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20ongoing%20battles%2C%20he%20voiced%20grave%20fears%20for%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20will%20see%20a%20kind%20of%20rescue%20operation%20like%20the%20kinds%20we%20see%20in%20our%20show%2C%20to%20bring%20back%20alive%20all%20the%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20newspaper%20writer%20who%20specialises%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20conflict%2C%20Issacharoff%20said%20he%20was%20baffled%20by%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20that%20blindsided%20and%20shocked%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20good%20explanation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believed%20Hamas%20had%20%26quot%3Bchanged%20over%20the%20years%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20become%20%26quot%3Bmore%20radical%20and%20more%20indoctrinated%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699943880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%