3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpecifically%2C%20fares%20to%20the%20Hyderabad%20airport%20and%20from%20the%20airport%20are%20quite%20low%20for%20the%20drivers%3B%20the%20fare%20only%20covers%20the%20fuel%20charges%2C%20leading%20to%20these%20protests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20constant%20demand%20from%20the%20union%20has%20been%20to%20make%20the%20platform%20companies%20give%20back%20the%20data%20of%20the%20trips%20back%20to%20the%20platform%20workers.%20In%20a%20recent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defindia.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FData-Justic-Book_For-website.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublication%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Shaik%20Saluddin%20argued%20that%20as%20partners%20of%20these%20platforms%2C%20workers%20need%20to%20be%20supplied%20with%20information%20as%20the%20company%20would%20do%20during%20an%20initial%20public%20offering.%20The%20union%20has%20questioned%20the%20information%20asymmetry%20being%20created%20by%20the%20companies.%20It%20wants%20the%20drivers%20to%20have%20their%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20platform%20workers%20are%20also%20aware%20of%20how%20the%20algorithms%20are%20taking%20control%20of%20their%20lives%20and%20have%20been%20demanding%20changes%20on%20who%20gets%20a%20trip%20allocated.%20Platforms%20could%20be%20allocating%20more%20work%20to%20workers%20who%20have%20taken%20a%20loan%20or%20have%20enrolled%20into%20different%20programmes%20by%20platform%20companies.%20This%20understanding%20of%20the%20rating%20algorithms%20is%20what%20makes%20the%20platform%20workers%20to%20demand%205%20star%20ratings%20from%20the%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20the%20issue%20of%20lower%20fare%20or%20being%20discriminated%20against%20by%20the%20algorithms%2C%20platform%20workers%20are%20questioning%20their%20digital%20exile%20from%20the%20platforms.%20Their%20platform%20worker%20IDs%20are%20blocked%20for%20protesting%2C%20or%20receiving%20complaints%20from%20customers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telangana%20Gig%20and%20Platform%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Union%20deals%20with%20an%20average%20of%2025-30%20workers%20whose%20IDs%20are%20blocked%20by%20the%20platforms.%20Most%20of%20the%20workers%20are%20unaware%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20blocks%2C%20and%20getting%20IDs%20unblocked%20is%20a%20tedious%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20alienation%20of%20workers%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20platforms%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20work%20in%20conditions%20that%20are%20not%20always%20in%20their%20favour.%20The%20union%20wants%20a%20grievance%20redressal%20platform%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20of%20drivers.%20In%20addition%2C%20they%20have%20been%20demanding%20for%20customer%20KYC%20(know%20your%20customer)%2C%20because%20customers%20themselves%20could%20behave%20unruly.%20How%20society%20has%20been%20treating%20platform%20workers%20without%20the%20dignity%20they%20deserve%20is%20often%20reflected%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20disagreements%20between%20the%20worker%20and%20the%20unruly%20demands%20of%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20platform%20workers%20face%20exploitation%20in%20terms%20of%20fair%20pay%2C%20they%20also%20lack%20support%20from%20the%20welfare%20institutions%20in%20Telangana.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20Telangana%20cancelled%20ration%20cards%20of%20people%20owning%20a%20car.%20It%20also%20cancelled%20access%20to%20ration%20for%20all%20car-owning%20drivers%20too.%20Access%20to%20accident%20insurance%2C%20state%20welfare%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20work%20conditions%20are%20a%20constant%20issue%20of%20concern%20for%20platform%20workers%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202023%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffair.work%2Fen%2Ffw%2Fpublications%2Ffairwork-india-ratings-2023-labour-standards-in-the-platform-economy%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Fairwork%20Project%20on%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20platform%20workers%20presents%20the%20current%20status%20of%20workers%20across%20India.%20It%20scores%20platform%20companies%20across%20different%20areas%20like%20pay%2C%20conditions%20of%20work%2C%20management%2C%20contracts%20and%20representation.%20The%20report%20shows%20how%20alienation%20of%20workers%20continues%20to%20occur%20in%20India%20amplified%20with%20algorithms%2C%20consumer%20rating%20and%20lack%20of%20government%20regulation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlatform%20companies%20push%20back%20against%20government%20regulation%20while%20employing%20union-busting%20methods%20such%20as%20blocking%20IDs%20and%20giving%20incentives%20to%20workers%20on%20the%20day%20of%20a%20strike%20announcement.%20While%20the%20unions%E2%80%99%20struggle%20to%20hold%20platforms%20accountable%20continues%2C%20the%20platforms%20themselves%20are%20also%20pushing%20for%20new%20forms%20of%20alternatives%20to%20unions%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faapti.in%2Fblog%2Fbuilding-the-driver-advisory-council%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edriver%20advisory%20councils%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20unions%20gain%20prominence%20and%20political%20parties%20show%20willingness%20to%20address%20platform%20workers%E2%80%99%20concerns%2C%20the%20era%20of%20unregulated%20platforms%20appears%20to%20be%20ending.%20The%20upcoming%20Telangana%20elections%20could%20also%20decide%20whether%20a%20change%20in%20the%20government%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20welfare%20law%20for%20workers.%20The%20platform%20workers%20are%20optimistic%20and%20have%20clearly%20said%20that%20their%20vote%20will%20go%20to%20the%20political%20parties%20that%20would%20address%20their%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20commerc