egins%20to%20feel%20like%20an%20obligation%20towards%20the%20cinematic%20universe%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98spyverse%E2%80%99%20as%20producers%20YRF%20calls%20this%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20in%20the%20care%20and%20affection%20to%20set%20these%20sequences%20up%20in%20the%20respective%20films%2C%20also%20ends%20up%20being%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20films.%20While%20Anand%E2%80%99s%20film%20felt%20like%20it%20had%20light%20feet%20and%20coasted%20on%20charm%2C%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20film%20feels%20stodgy%2C%20bearing%20the%20weight%20of%20a%20star%2C%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20wish%20to%20take%20even%20the%20smallest%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FvEjTUDjjU6A%3Fsi%3DE0_9Zl2iUkzYQ9ZL%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20Maneesh%20Sharma%20has%20never%20imposed%20a%20signature%20on%20his%20films.%20While%20that%20can%20often%20be%20an%20asset%20for%20a%20franchise%20film%2C%20a%20director%E2%80%99s%20less-than-distinct%20vision%20is%20also%20revealed%20fairly%20quickly.%20Like%20it%20often%20does%20for%20spies%2C%20the%20past%20comes%20back%20for%20Zoya%20and%20Tiger.%20A%20disenchanted%20patriot%20(Emraan%20Hashmi)%2C%20comes%20for%20the%20two%20super%20spies%20and%20their%20son%2C%20unimaginatively%20called%20Junior.%20What%20follows%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20renegade%20missions%2C%20the%20spectacular%20line%20around%20the%20interval%20point%20%E2%80%9CZoya%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhi%20ne%20%3C%2Fem%3ETiger%3Cem%3E%20bhai%20ko%20dhokha%20de%20diya%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20(Did%20Zoya%20bhabhi%20betray%20Tiger%20bhai%3F)%20and%20a%20maniac%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98vision%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20future%20of%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20we%E2%80%99re%20watching%20an%20extravagant%20spy%20film