20radical%20Pakistani%20army%20and%20peace-loving%20Pakistanis%20is%20made%20more%20than%20once.%20Tiger%20keeps%20referring%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20as%20his%20%3Cem%3Emaayka%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20married%20woman%E2%80%99s%20mother%E2%80%99s%20home)%20%E2%80%93%20an%20endearing%20touch.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20moment%20really%20arrives%2C%20Tiger%203%20isn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20hide%20its%20intent%20to%20ride%20the%20wave%20of%20hideous%20jingoism.%20It%20becomes%20visible%20in%20a%20choice%20%E2%80%93%20when%20an%20ISI%20agent%20is%20shot%20dead%2C%20but%20the%20R%26amp%3BAW%20spy%E2%80%99s%20throat%20is%20sliced%20open.%20The%20good-natured%2C%20peace-loving%20Pakistani%20prime%20minister%20(Simran)%20kicks%20off%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20independence%20day%20celebrations%20with%20the%20Indian%20national%20anthem.%20Even%20for%20a%20Salman%20Khan%20film%2C%20and%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20times%20when%20patriotic%20fantasies%20seem%20to%20know%20no%20bounds%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pathaan%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20paraphrases%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20in%20the%20climax%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20soldier%20asks%20what%20they%20can%20do%20for%20their%20country%2C%20not%20what%20a%20country%20can%20do%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%20In%20Salman%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%20where%20the%20stakes%20for%20million%20dollar%20set-pieces%20feel%20inconsequential%2C%20the%20emotional%20beats%20feel%20insincere%20and%20the%20patriotism%20almost%20begins%20to%20seem%20like%20a%20surrogate%20to%20the%20country%20asking%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20more%20can%20we%20do%20to%20further%20Salman%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20swagger%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20of%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20156%20minutes%20are%20comatose%20though.%20Salman%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Tiger%20has%20one%20moment%20of%20grace.%20Hurtling%20down%20using%20a%20parachute%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Pathaan%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20reminded%20how%20the%20two%20super%2