20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20looking%20ahead%20may%20be%20a%20pointless%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tournament%20that%20saw%20the%20defending%20champions%20being%20pulped%20to%20dust%20in%20the%20league%20stages%20and%20most%20matches%20lacking%20in%20competitive%20edge%2C%20this%20World%20Cup%20could%20be%20seen%20among%20the%20most%20boring%20ever.%20The%2050-over%20format%20was%20conceived%20and%20designed%20to%20supplement%20Test%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20dwindling%20revenues%20in%20the%201970s%20and%20five%20decades%20later%20its%20very%20relevance%20is%20now%20being%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20has%20moved%20forward.%20It%20has%20too%20many%20things%20to%20do%2C%20too%20many%20distractions%20to%20engage%20with.%20Time%2C%20that%20most%20feared%20entity%20mankind%20has%20ever%20invented%2C%20functions%20in%20a%20specific%20context.%20If%20a%20one-day%20contest%20was%20earlier%20seen%20as%20the%20most%20crude%20slam-bang%20version%20of%20a%20nuanced%2C%20long-drawn%20battle%20of%20skills%20called%20Tests%2C%20today%20its%20survival%20is%20being%20threatened%20by%20the%20T20%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20The%20breathless%20pace%20of%20the%2020-over%20format%20has%20sucked%20the%20spectators%20into%20a%20world%20where%20for%20three%20hours%2C%20time%20ceases%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronic%20it%20may%20be%2C%20but%20what%20was%20once%20called%20%E2%80%9Cpyjama%E2%80%9D%20cricket%20%E2%80%93%20indicating%20that%20it%20was%20non-serious%20%E2%80%93%20has%20today%20many%20defenders%20who%20see%20in%20it%20the%20same%20nuances%20as%20they%20had%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20The%20shock%2C%20and%20even%20awe%2C%20that%20the%20brutal%2C%20endless%20hitting%20of%20the%20ball%20evokes%20in%20Twenty20%20cricket%2C%20leaves%20little%20scope%20for%20reflection%2C%20pause%2C%20strategising%20and%20planning.%20In%20this%20fierce%20battle%20of%20who%20takes%20less%20time%20to%20kill%2C%20there%20is%20no%20time%20for%20a%20magical%20knock%20of%20epic%20immensity%20that%20Glen%20Maxwell%20played%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%20this%20World%20Cup.%20Even%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccrippled%E2%80%9D%20Maxwell%20needed%20that%20space%20and%20time%20that%20only%20a%2050-over%20format%20could%20have%20provided%20him%20with.%20To%20create%20a%20fantasy%20world%20from%20real%20ingredients%20Maxwell%20needed%20time%2C%20that%20the%20T20%20format%20would%20have%20denied%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAgainst%20the%20odds%20%F0%9F%99%8C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stats%20behind%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20ODI%20knocks%20ever%20%F0%9F%93%B2%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Frv0UVeOWYZ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Frv0UVeOWYZ%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FF5LI5xGEXv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FF5LI5xGEXv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20(%40cricketworldcup)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcricketworldcup%2Fstatus%2F1722149672335147148%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%E2%80%9Cboring%E2%80%9D%20World%20Cup%20makes%20you%20realise%20how%20much%20T20%20cricket%20has%20impacted%20our%20senses%20and%20how%20little%20the%20newer%20spectators%20care%20about%20what%20building%20an%20innings%20mean.%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20that%20epitome%20of%20how%20an%20innings%20should%20be%20crafted%20and%20taken%20to%20a%20crescendo%2C%20is%20that%20perfect%20Test%20and%20one-day%20batsman%2C%20who%20may%20not%20be%20too%20%E2%80%9Crelevant%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20shortest%20version%20of%20the%20game.%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20special%20skills%20lie%20in%20his%20understanding%20of%20the%20conditions%2C%20the%20match%20situation%2C%20and%20how%20well%20he%20shapes%20his%20responses%20to%20them%2C%20as%20he%20has%20shown%20umpteen%20times%20this%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET20%20are%20shorn%20of%20middle%20overs%20that%20the%2050-over%20format%20needs%20special%20care%20and%20understanding%20to%20deal%20with%2C%20be%20it%20the%20batsman%20or%20the%20bowler.%20It%20may%20be%20an%20apt%20statement%20to%20make%20that%20whichever%20team%20controls%20the%20middle%20overs%20controls%20the%20match.%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20Adam%20Zampa%2C%20Indians%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20South%20African%20Keshav%20Maharaj%20and%20New%20Zealand%E2%80%99s%20Mitchel%20Santner%20are%20the%20best%20examples%20of%20bowlers%20who%20have%20won%20the%20game%20for%20their%20teams%20in%20the%20middle%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-bowling-attack-diverse-and-deadly-cricket-world-cup%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Bowling%20Attack%2C%20Diverse%20and%20Deadly%2C%20Is%20Fuelling%20World%20Cup%20Run%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20the%20very%20loveable%20and%20resilient%20Afghanistan%20team%20which%20has%20lent%20this%20tournament%20a%20unique%20flavour.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20the%20shorter%20the%20contest%2C%20the%20shorter%20the%20gap%20between%20a%20good%20and%20bad%20team%2C%20but%20the%20impact%20that%20this%20Afghan%20team%20has%20left%20with%20their%20passionate%20involvement%20and%20sharp%20skills%2C%20be%20it%20in%20batting%20or%20bowling%2C%20would%20have%20been%20difficult%20to%20replicate%20in%20the%20T20%20format.%20So%20much%20has%20been%20written%20about%20them%20in%20Indian%20and%20even%20foreign%20papers%2C%20that%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20highlight%20any%20new%20fact%20that%20readers%20would%20not%C2%A0%20already%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20stayed%20with%20me%20is%20not%20just%20their%20professional%20outlook%20even%20while%20they%20exhibited%20their%20joyous%20spirit%20but%20the%20very%20%E2%80%9Cmelodious%20%E2%80%9C%20names%20which%20followers%20of%20Hindi%20film%20lyrics%20of%20the%2050s%20and%2060s%20would%20be%20very%20familiar%20with.%20Noor%20(light)%2C%20Nabi%20(prophet)%2C%20Rashid%20(rationale%2C%20intelligent)%2C%20Rahmat%20(mercy%2C%20compassion)%2C%20Azmat%20(magnificent)%20are%20some%20of%20the%20names%20of%20their%20key%20players.%20They%20remind%20you%20of%20a%20time%20when%20Urdu%2C%20Farsi%20and%20Hindi%20would%20combine%20to%20lend%20Hindi%20films%20a%20spirit%20of%20inclusivity%20so%20missing%20in%20our%20present%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20harping%20on%20Afghan%20names%20may%20seem%20a%20digression%20from%20the%20main%20theme%20and%20that%20is%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20%C2%A050-over%20format.%20Perhaps%20this%20format%20needs%20a%20bit%20of%20loosening%20up%2C%20less%20restrictions%20and%20greater%20freedom%20for%20captains%20to%20plan%20their%20strategies.%20It%20is%20up%20to%20administrators%20and%20the%20players%20to%20join%20hands%20and%20to%20chalk%20out%20a%20way%20forward.%20People%20play%20and%20watch%20cricket%20for%20the%20unique%20set%20of%20skills%20it%20requires%20and%20is%20on%20display.%20Profit%20and%20revenues%20cannot%20be%20the%20only%20guiding%20principle%20of%20the%20administrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpradeep-magazine%5C%22%3EPradeep%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20cricket%20writer%20and%20the%20author%20of%20two%20books%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ENot%20Quite%20Cricket%3Cem%3E%20and%20the%20recently%20published%3C%2Fem%3E%20Not%20Just%20Cricket%2C%20A%20Reporter%E2%80%99s%20Journey%20Through%20Modern%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699939129000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14104648%2FF-QTBwxW8AASwIh.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fextra-cover-cricket-world-cup-2023-boring%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20play%20and%20watch%20cricket%20for%20the%20unique%20set%20of%20skills%