cent%20turmoil%20in%20her%20life%20was%20retaliation%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-weisselberg-refuses-to-be-silenced-trump-investigation-manhattan-da-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20cooperation%20in%20the%20fraud%20convictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20her%20former%20father-in-law%20and%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-weisselberg-trump-org-cfo-worried-about-prosecutors-2018-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShe%20began%20working%20with%20prosecutors%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20fraud%20case%20against%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20in%202021%2C%20speaking%20with%20the%20media%20and%20providing%20crucial%20financial%20documents%20that%20led%20to%20her%20former%20father-in-law's%20eventual%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20she%20was%20also%20battling%20an%20eviction%20order%20for%20her%20Upper%20West%20Side%20apartment%2C%20which%20Allen%20Weisselberg%20had%20arranged%20for%20her%20after%20her%202018%20divorce%20from%20his%20son%2C%20Barry%20Weisselberg.%20The%20couple%20was%20also%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20custody%20battle%2C%20she%20told%20The%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20their%20divorce%2C%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20and%20her%20ex-husband%20lived%20for%2010%20years%20rent-free%20in%20a%20glamorous%20Central%20Park%20South%20apartment%20provided%20to%20them%20as%20an%20untaxed%20perk%20from%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20were%20friendly%20with%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20who%20invited%20them%20to%20his%202017%20inauguration%20and%20also%20signed%20some%20of%20the%20Weisselberg's%20kids'%20tuition%20checks%20%E2%80%94%20further%20evidence%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanhattan-da-trump-signed-tuition-checks-allen-weisselberg-kids-2021-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DProsecutors%2520said%2520that%2520from%25202012%2Caccount%2520of%2520the%2520Donald%2520J%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20untaxed%20compensation%20normalized%20within%20the%20Trump%20Organization%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20in%20Allen%20Weisselberg's%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Barry%20Weisselberg%20filed%20for%20divorce%2C%20his%20father%20put%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20up%20in%20a%20new%20apartment%20managed%20by%20a%20real%20estate%20magnate%20known%20to%20for%20its%20frequent%20evictions%2C%20The%20Nation%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Weisselberg%20acknowledged%20that%20she%20struggled%20to%20make%20the%20%246%2C050%20rent%20in%20the%20new%20place%2C%20especially%20because%20many%20of%20the%20perks%20she%20was%20accustomed%20to%20in%20her%20marriage%20were%20not%20accessible%20to%20her%20in%20the%20divorce%2C%20she%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEviction%20proceedings%20against%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20began%20in%20October%202020%20with%20Allen%20Weisselberg%20listed%20as%20her%20guarantor.%20But%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months%20%E2%80%94%20as%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20began%20speaking%20publicly%20with%20the%20media%20about%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20%E2%80%94%20the%20lawsuit%20against%20Jennifer%20and%20Allen%20Weisselberg%20shifted%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarry%20Weisselberg%20didn't%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%20An%20attorney%20for%20Allen%20Weisselberg%20also%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attorney%20for%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg's%20landlord%20discontinued%20the%20New%20York%20County%20Civil%20Court%20action%20against%20her%20and%20Allen%20in%20April%202021%20and%20filed%20new%20eviction%20proceedings%20against%20just%20Jennifer%20alone%20in%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20May%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20struggled%20to%20afford%20lawyers%20during%20this%20period%20and%20told%20The%20Nation%20she%20had%20to%20defend%20herself%20at%20times%2C%20all%20the%20while%2C%20her%20ex-husband's%20dad%20was%20covering%20his%20legal%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20signed%20a%20settlement%20agreement%20to%20pay%20back%20half%20the%20rent%20she%20owed%20and%20move%20out.%20She%20was%20officially%20evicted%20in%20April%20of%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBarry%20told%20me%20he%20wants%20me%20homeless%2C%20without%20my%20kids%2C%20so%20I%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Florida%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20she's%20from%2C%20she%20told%20The%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20while%2C%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20has%20been%20battling%20Barry%20for%20custody%20of%20the%20couple's%20two%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Weisselberg%20previously%20sought%20and%20won%20a%20domestic%20violence%20protection%20order%20against%20Barry%20Weisselberg%2C%20though%20it%20was%20later%20vacated%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20physical%20custody%20of%20the%20kids%20in%20February%202020%20before%20she%20began%20cooperating%20with%20lawyers.%20A%20psychiatrist%20ordered%20to%20evaluate%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20before%20Barry%20took%20the%20kids%20found%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bmanic%20psychotic%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20per%20The%20Nation.%20She%20told%20the%20outlet%20she%20was%20taken%20but%20not%20admitted%20to%20Bellevue%20Hospital%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20since%20lost%20all%20custody%20and%20visitation%20rights%20with%20her%20kids%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20her%20home%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20evident%20proof%20that%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg's%20bad%20luck%20is%20retaliation%20for%20her%20cooperation%20in%20the%20case%20against%20the%20Trump%20Organization%2C%20an%20unnamed%20official%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20Manhattan%20DA's%20office%20with%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20on%20the%20cases%20involving%20Allen%20Weisselberg%20and%20the%20Trump%20Org%20told%20The%20Nation%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20credible%20that%20they're%20retaliating%20against%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20also%20acknowledging%20that%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20may%20have%20been%20the%20harbinger%20of%20her%20own%20bad%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Weisselberg%20told%20The%20Nation%20she%20believed%20speaking%20out%20against%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20would%20help%20her%20get%20her%20kids%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20she%20is%20still%20searching%20for%20a%20permanent%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-weisselberg-lost-home-kids-after-cooperating-trump-organization-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699937357000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6552ca6a58cf5fbccb95f1c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-weisselberg-lost-home-kids-after-cooperating-trump-organization-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20was%20evicted%20from%20her%20home%2C%20and%20lost%20custody%20of%20her%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20she%20thinks%20it's%20retaliation%20for%20blowing%20the%20the%20whistle%20on%20the%20Trump%20Org.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Eliza%20Goodwin%2CErin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-weisselberg-lost-home-kids-after-cooperating-trump-organization-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Korea%20fears%20Hamas-style%20attack%20from%20the%20North%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699937278000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1473B%2Fproduction%2F_131717738_3ab863af-1024-46a4-b13b-b153c0d5b11b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22h