aj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%20but%20admits%20that%20unemployment%20is%20a%20major%20point%20of%20concern.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20unemployment.%20Otherwise%2C%20other%20things%20are%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091410%2FPSX_20231112_040204-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091410%2FPSX_20231112_040204-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091410%2FPSX_20231112_040204-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091410%2FPSX_20231112_040204-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684595%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDaily-wage%20workers%20assembled%20at%20a%20crossing%20in%20Indore%2C%20MP%20in%20search%20of%20work.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20prepares%20to%20vote%20on%20November%2017%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20employment%20weighs%20heavily%20upon%20the%20Chouhan%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20voting%20depends%20on%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors%20and%20complicated%20regional%20and%20state-level%20calculations%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20unmissable%20as%20one%20moves%20in%20the%20state%20are%20the%20common%20grievances%20of%20inflation%20and%20unemployment.%20In%20fact%2C%20these%20two%20related%20issues%20are%20among%20the%20most%20common%20factors%20mentioned%20by%20critics%20of%20the%20Shivraj%20government%20for%20voting%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20the%20construction%20workers%20in%20Indore%2C%20cotton-yarn%20factory%20staff%20in%20Sehore%2C%20the%20illiterate%20daily-wage%20labourer%20in%20Sagar%20or%20the%20government%20job%20applicants%20across%20regions%2C%20the%20Chouhan%20government%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20have%20transformed%20MP%20from%20a%20BIMARU%20(an%20abbreviation%20for%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20considered%20low%20on%20key%20prosperity%20indicators)%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebemisaal%3C%2Fem%3E%20state%20in%2018%20years%20of%20rule%2C%20is%20facing%20difficult%20questions%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20livelihood.%20The%20Congress%20is%20banking%20on%20the%20discontent%20of%20the%20youth%20and%20unemployed%20people%20for%20change%20in%20power%2C%20and%20a%20major%20line%20of%20its%20attack%20against%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20raising%20the%20numerous%20cases%20of%20irregularities%2C%20termed%20%E2%80%98scams%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20opposition%20and%20media%2C%20in%20recruitment%20for%20government%20jobs.%20The%20alleged%20corruption%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process%20under%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%20says%2C%20has%20impeded%20the%20process%20of%20providing%20employment%20to%20educated%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20election%20manifesto%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20it%20will%20bring%20in%20a%20law%20to%20better%20manage%20recruitments%2C%20%E2%80%98MP%20Sarkari%20Bharti%20Kanoon%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20provide%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20Rs%2C%203%2C000%20monthly%20stipend%20to%20unemployed%20youth%2C%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%20The%20party%20has%20drawn%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20last%20few%20years%20of%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20have%20been%20marred%20by%20paper%20leaks%20in%20competitive%20exams%2C%20examinations%20not%20being%20conducted%20as%20per%20law%20and%20results%20not%20being%20declared%20due%20to%20legal%20disputes.%20A%20new%20law%20would%20be%20brought%20in%20to%20ensure%20that%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20incidents%20are%20not%20repeated%20in%20future%20and%20there%20is%20transparency%20in%20government%20recruitment%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20said%20in%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promise%20of%20a%20proposed%20recruitment%20law%20appeals%20to%20government%20job%20aspirants%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20since%202021%20been%20demanding%20such%20a%20measure%20at%20the%20state-level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJab%20%3C%2Fem%3Ematch%3Cem%3E%20hi%20fixed%20hai%2C%20koi%20khelke%20matlab%20nahi%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(What%20use%20is%20it%20playing%20a%20game%20when%20the%20outcome%20is%20already%20manipulated)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kapil%20Jat%2C%20a%20government%20job%20aspirant%20from%20Sehore.%20His%20statement%20reveals%20the%20disenchantment%20created%20among%20the%20youth%20by%20the%20irregularities%20and%20frauds%20in%20recruitment%20processes%20for%20government%20jobs%20under%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20in%20its%20last%20two%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20a%20year%20after%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20wrested%20power%20back%20from%20the%20Congress%20through%20mass%20defections%2C%20Jat%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20examination%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Rural%20Agricultural%20Extension%20Officer%20or%20RAEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20examination%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20tests%2C%20Senior%20Agricultural%20Development%20Officer%20and%20nursing%2C%20was%20cancelled%20after%20the%20question%20paper%20was%20leaked.%20The%20paper%20had%20been%20downloaded%20in%20an%20unauthorised%20manner%2C%20said%20officials.%20The%20exam%20was%20held%20again%20but%20Jat%20failed%20to%20qualify%20and%20generally%20lost%20motivation.%20What%20bothers%20him%20more%20is%20that%20the%20culprits%20behind%20the%20leak%20were%20not%20punished.%20Jat%2C%20who%20holds%20an%20MSc%C2%A0degree%20in%20agriculture%2C%20is%20working%20as%20a%20guest%20teacher%20in%20a%20school%20in%20Dewas.%20But%20he%20is%20not%20content%20with%20his%20job%20he%20took%20up%20in%20desperation.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20earning%20only%20Rs.%209%2C000.%20Had%20the%20RAEO%20exams%20been%20held%20in%20a%20fair%20manner%20I%20could%20have%20qualified%20and%20started%20with%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%2035%2C000.%20These%20%5Bscams%20in%20recruitment%20process%5D%20are%20really%20causing%20us%20big%20harm%20and%20wasting%20precious%20years%20of%20our%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Clear%20fraud%E2%80%99%3A%20More%20examination%20irregularities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20infamous%20Vyapam%20Scam%20in%20pre-medical%20recruitment%20stained%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20government%20from%202013-2018%2C%20his%20tenure%20from%202020%20was%20hit%20by%20allegations%20of%20fresh%20irregularities%20in%20other%20examinations.%20To%20name%20a%20few%2C%20the%20recruitment%20of%20contractual%20nursing%20staff%20under%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20and%20the%20recruitment%20process%20of%20Patwaris%20(revenue%20department%20staffers).%20The%20%E2%80%9CPatwari%C2%A0Recruitment%20Scam%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20it%20was%20labelled%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20came%20to%20light%20after%20it%20was%20found%20that%20seven%20out%20of%20the%20top%2010%20candidates%20who%20had%20taken%20the%20online%20examination%20for%20the%20recruitment%20came%20from%20the%20same%20exam%20centre%20in%20Gwalior%2C%20a%20college%20run%20by%20a%20BJP%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20it%20was%20also%20found%20that%20the%20toppers%20in%20the%20examination%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20answers%20to%20basic%20questions%20and%20many%20of%20those%20who%20had%20scored%20high%20marks%20in%20English%20had%20signed%20in%20Hindi.%20Facing%20a%20demand%20by%20the%20Congress%20for%20a%20CBI%20inquiry%2C%20Chouhan%20in%20July%20put%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20successful%20candidates.%20The%20scam%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20a%20retired%20High%20Court%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20case%2C%20in%20June%2C%20police%20booked%20more%20than%2070%20government%20school%20teachers%20in%20Morena%20district%20after%20it%20was%20found%20that%20they%20were%20appointed%20under%20the%20disability%20quota%20allegedly%20after%20securing%20disability%20certificates%20fraudulently.%C2%A0%20In%202022%2C%20candidates%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20MP%20TET%20(Teacher%20Eligibility%20Test)%20and%20police%20recruitment%20examination%20staged%20a%20protest%20outside%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20staff%20election%20board%2C%20alleging%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20Bishnoi%20(30)%20of%20Harda%20district%2C%20150%20km%20south%20of%20Bhopal%2C%20was%20among%20the%2010%20lakh%20applicants%20who%20sat%20for%20the%20examination%20in%202022%20to%20fill%208%2C500%20seats%20for%20Patwaris.%20He%20secured%20145%20marks%20in%20the%20Patwari%20examination%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20cut-off%20for%20selection%20by%20one%20mark.%20But%20he%20believes%20that%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20as%20the%20exams%20were%20not%20conducted%20in%20a%20fair%20manner.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20clear%20fraud%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20challenged%20the%20answers%20to%20three%20questions%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeterred%20by%20the%20scam%20in%20the%20Patwari%20recruitment%2C%20Bishnoi%20has%20shifted%20attention%20to%20preparing%20for%20the%20job%20of%20a%20police%20sub-inspector.%20He%20performs%20fairly%20well%20in%20the%20mock%20tests.%20But%20a%20vacancy%20for%20the%20sub-inspector%20post%20has%20not%20been%20advertised%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20result%20is%20that%20our%20careers%20get%20pushed%20back%20by%20at%20least%20five%20years.%20The%20last%20patwari%20exam%20was%20in%202017%20and%20then%202022.%20Even%20those%20who%20get%20selected%20in%20these%20exams%20go%20through%20unease%20as%20they%20think%20that%20even%20if%20they%20qualify%2C%20there%20will%20be%20some%20fraud%20that%20will%20obstruct%20their%20recruitment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAspirants%20also%20said%20that%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20the%20BJP%20government%20had%20a%20direct%20bearing%20on%20the%20career%20options%20of%20the%20youth%20as%20they%20involved%20recruitment%20for%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20different%20between%20the%20Vyapam%20scam%20in%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20previous%20government%20and%20the%20scams%20in%20the%20present%20government%20(2020-2023)%20is%20that%20the%20appointments%20under%20scanner%20today%20impact%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20people%2C%20including%20those%20from%20poorer%20and%20agrarian%20families%2C%20says%20Ranjit%20Raghunath%2C%20a%20recruitment%20activist%2C%20who%20has%20been%20campaigning%20in%20the%20state%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years%20for%20a%20law%20to%20check%20anomalies%20in%20such%20examination%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091358%2FPSX_20231112_040132-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091358%2FPSX_20231112_040132-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091358%2FPSX_20231112_040132-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091358%2FPSX_20231112_040132-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684594%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDaily-wage%20workers%20assembled%20at%20a%20crossing%20in%20Indore%2C%20MP%20in%20search%20of%20work.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20scams%20in%20the%20present%20government%20impact%20a%20large%20range%20of%20people.%20It%20directly%20impacts%20the%20people%20in%20the%20villages%20and%20farming%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raghunath%20(28).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghunath%2C%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20National%20Educated%20Youth%20Union%20(NEYU)%2C%20a%20body%20that%20came%20into%20being%20following%20the%20growing%20discontent%20against%20recruitment%20scams%2C%20entered%20activism%20following%20his%20own%20bad%20experience.%20With%20a%20dream%20of%20becoming%20an%20agricultural%20officer%2C%20in%202021%20he%20sat%20for%20the%20examination%20of%20the%20AREO%20which%20was%20cancelled%20due%20to%20paper%20leak.%20Raghunath%20hails%20from%20a%20farming%20background%20in%20Dewas.%20His%20father%20sold%20wawa%20for%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellation%20of%20the%20exam%20due%20to%20paper%20leak%20made%20him%20doubt%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20exams%20under%20the%20current%20system%2C%20and%20eventually%20motivated%20him%20to%20search%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%20solution.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CCancelling%20a%20particular%20exam%20is%20not%20the%20answer.%20All%20these%20scamsters%20enjoy%20some%20patronage%2C%20although%20I%20cannot%20say%20at%20what%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEYU%20has%20demanded%20that%20an%20independent%20state%20recruitment%20commission%20be%20constituted%20for%20recruitment%20purposes%2C%20and%20that%20the%20CBI%20or%20an%20SIT%20investigate%20such%20scams%20whenever%20they%20surface.%20The%20NEYU%2C%20which%20submitted%20a%20draft%20of%20a%20proposed%20law%20to%20both%20the%20main%20parties%2C%20also%20wants%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20Rs.%205%2C000%20as%20monetary%20assistance%20per%20month%20to%20each%20unemployed%20youth%20if%20they%20are%20without%20a%20job%20even%20a%20year%20after%20graduation%20or%20post-graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Only%20the%20rich%20get%20selected%E2%80%99%3A%20Big%20setbacks%20and%20disillusionment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tap%20into%20the%20anger%20among%20the%20unemployed%20and%20under-employed%20youth%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20implement%20a%20Right%20to%20Employment%20in%20the%20state%20and%20fill%20two%20lakh%20vacant%20posts%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%20The%20party%20said%20it%20would%20run%20a%20campaign%20to%20fill%20the%20posts%20of%20teachers%2C%20patwaris%2C%20police%20personnel%2C%20Anganwadi%20workers%2C%20nurses%20and%20forest%20guards%20left%20vacant%20in%20the%20last%2018%20years%20of%20BJP%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20probe%20the%20irregularities%20and%20corruption%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%20through%20a%20commission%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20high%20court%20judge%20and%20launch%20a%20fresh%20investigation%20into%20the%20high-profile%20Vyapam%20scam%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Patwari%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJob%20aspirants%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0spoke%20to%20said%20that%20the%20repeated%20cases%20of%20corruption%20in%20recruitment%20examinations%20have%20created%20a%20climate%20where%20they%20have%20started%20questioning%20the%20credibility%20of%20such%20tests.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%99If%20an%20exam%20is%20held%20under%20this%20government%2C%20there%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20some%20irregularity%20or%20fraud%20that%20will%20come%20up%2C%E2%80%99%20this%20is%20the%20common%20refrain%20among%20students%20and%20aspirants%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20aspirant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghunath%20further%20said%20that%20the%20scams%20have%20sent%20a%20negative%20message%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20aspirants%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20from%20farming%20and%20working-class%20backgrounds%2C%20that%20their%20sons%20and%20daughters%20could%20not%20get%20selected%20for%20government%20jobs%20due%20to%20the%20corruption.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20started%20to%20believe%20that%20seats%20are%20sold%20and%20only%20the%20rich%20get%20selected%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghunath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%20this%20year%2C%20the%20government%20informed%20the%20MP%20Assembly%20that%20the%20state%20had%2039%20lakh%20registered%20unemployed%20persons%2C%20a%20big%20jump%20from%20the%2025.8%20lakh%20unemployed%20persons%20as%20on%20April%201%2C%202022%2C%20majority%20of%20them%20from%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20reported%20Times%20of%20India.%20Throughout%20her%20MP%20campaign%2C%20Congress%20national%20general%20secretary%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20has%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20only%20provided%2021%20government%20jobs%2C%20although%20a%20recent%20report%20in%20The%20Indian%20Express%20suggested%20that%20the%20government%20pegged%20the%20number%20at%2061%2C000%20as%20it%20included%20numbers%20from%20its%20skill-development%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Chouhan%20promised%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20retained%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20it%20would%20provide%20a%20job%20to%20each%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20statements%20have%20done%20little%20to%20appease%20voters%20like%20Inder%20Bai%20Chauhan%20in%20Sehore%20district.%20She%20recently%20lost%20her%20job%20at%20a%20cotton%20spinning%20unit%20and%20has%20been%20unemployed%20since.%20She%20has%20not%20even%20been%20paid%20her%20dues%2C%20despite%20several%20protests%20by%20workers.%20After%20a%20decade%20of%20work%2C%20Inder%20Bai%20had%20managed%20to%20climb%20the%20ranks%20and%20was%20earning%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%2014%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20much-publicised%20Ladli%20Behna%20flagship%20scheme%20of%20Chouhan%2C%20under%20which%20eligible%20adult%20women%20get%20a%20monthly%20stipend%20of%20Rs.%201%2C000%20(now%20increased%20to%20Rs.%201%2C250)%20provides%20her%20no%20solace.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20will%20we%20run%20our%20house%20in%20Rs.%201000%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwasnt-my-mother-your-ladli-behna-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Wasn%E2%80%99t%20My%20Mother%20Your%20Ladli%20Behna%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20unemployment%20and%20rising%20costs%20of%20living%20have%20upset%20voters%20across%20the%20spectrum%2C%20how%20much%20of%20it%20translates%20into%20votes%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Congress%2C%20is%20something%20only%20the%20results%20on%20December%203%20will%20reveal%20given%20the%20tight%20fight%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%20Many%20voters%20indicated%20that%20despite%20the%20financial%20crunch%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20voting%2C%20they%20could%20consider%20other%20factors%20as%20well.%20Bishnoi%20said%20despite%20his%20resentment%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbest%20among%20the%20worst.%E2%80%9D%20A%20construction%20worker%2C%20Mahendra%2C%20struggling%20to%20find%20regular%20work%20in%20Indore%2C%20said%20the%20law%20and%20order%20had%20improved%20under%20the%20BJP%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20expects%20the%20issue%20to%20play%20out%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Shobha%20Oza%20said%20unemployment%20was%20a%20big%20issue%20in%20this%20election%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20sending%20the%20education%20system%20in%20the%20state%20for%20a%20toss.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dreams%20of%20these%20applicants%20have%20received%20a%20big%20setback%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPankaj%20Chaturvedi%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20from%202020%20to%202023%2C%20the%20government%20had%20taken%20steps%20to%20provide%201%20lakh%20jobs%20each%20year%20and%20initiated%20measures%20such%20as%20SKY%20(Seekho%20Kamao%20Yojana)%20for%20skill%20development%20and%20on-the-job%20training.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20BJP%20is%20sincerely%20trying%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20and%20training%20the%20youth%20to%20not%20just%20get%20jobs%20but%20also%20become%20job%20creators%2C%20the%20Congress%20still%20talks%20about%20providing%20berozgari%20bhatta%20(unemployment%20doles)%20to%20these%20youth%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chaturvedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20could%20also%20find%20some%20solace%20in%20the%20falling%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20annual%20report%20of%20the%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20published%20by%20the%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20Office%20for%20the%20period%20July%202022%20to%20June%202023%20said%20that%20MP%20had%20an%20unemployment%20rate%20of%204.4.%20The%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20the%20urban%20areas%20was%2013.1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20during%20the%20period%202018-19%20was%2010.4%2C%20with%20urban%20unemployment%20rate%20at%2021.9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2011%2C%20the%20BJP%20released%20its%20election%20manifesto%2C%20making%20a%20slew%20of%20welfare%20promises%20directed%20at%20farmers%20and%20women.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20mention%20of%20dealing%20with%20unemployment.%20All%20that%20BJP%20President%20J.P%20Nadda%20said%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20manifesto%20was%20that%20if%20voted%20back%20to%20power%20the%20government%20would%20provide%20job%20opportunities%20to%20%E2%80%9Calmost%20every%20family%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20government%20sector%20or%20self-employment.%20Otherwise%2C%20much%20of%20his%20address%20was%20directed%20at%20comparing%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20two%20decades%20in%20power%20in%20MP%20with%20the%20previous%20governments%20run%20by%20the%20Congress.%20The%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20MP%20had%20increased%20from%20Rs.%2011%2C717%20in%202003%20to%20Rs.%201.40%20lakh%20in%202023%2C%20he%20said.%20To%20further%20push%20his%20narrative%2C%20Nadda%20said%20he%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20Rewa%20in%20the%20Vindhya%20region%20of%20the%20state%20had%20purchased%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20motorbikes%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20shows%20how%20much%20the%20purchasing%20power%20of%20the%20farmers%20has%20increased%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nadda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20BJP%20released%20its%20manifesto%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20the%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20candidate%2C%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP%20through%20a%20post%20on%20X%20where%20he%20listed%20the%20top%20five%20promises%20made%20by%20his%20party%20to%20voters.%20The%20issue%20of%20jobs%20was%20at%20number%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20is%20going%20to%20fill%20two%20lakh%20vacant%20posts.%20What%20are%20you%20doing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nath%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20NEYU%20is%20appealing%20to%20students%20and%20youngsters%C2%A0to%20make%20their%20resentment%20felt%20through%20voting.%20How%20much%20of%20it%20reflects%20in%C2%A0an%C2%A0anti-incumbency%20vote%2C%20the%20EVMs%20will%20reveal%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699934497000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14091422%2FPSX_20231112_041724-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-jobs-unemployment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Be%20it%20construction%20workers%20in%20Indore%2C%20cotton-yarn%20factory%20staff%20in%20Sehore%2C%20the%20daily-wage%20labourer%20in%20Sagar%20or%20government%20job%20applicants%20across%20regions%2C%20the%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20BJP%20government's%20claims%20to%20have%20transformed%20MP%20from%20a%20'BIMARU'%20to%20'Bemisaal'%20are%20facing%20challenges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-jobs-unemployment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20businesses%20are%20pulling%20billions%20in%20profits%20from%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699934416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F108BB%2Fproduc