20which%20contain%20all%20manner%20of%20information%20on%20finances%2C%20taxes%2C%20health%20and%20professional%20data%2C%20including%20research.%20Yet%20India%20has%20hardly%20any%20legal%20procedures%20or%20guidelines%20when%20the%20police%20or%20other%20enforcement%20agencies%20seize%20your%20devices%20in%20the%20course%20of%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20democracies%2C%20whether%20in%20the%20US%20or%20Europe%2C%20do%20not%20allow%20the%20seizure%20of%20devices%20without%20a%20judicial%20warrant.%20Even%20after%20procuring%20a%20judicial%20warrant%2C%20police%20have%20to%20observe%20due%20process%20relating%20to%20the%20specificity%20of%20what%20information%20is%20to%20be%20extracted%2C%20and%20in%20what%20manner.%20Elaborate%20guidelines%20ensure%20that%20the%20constitutional%20guarantee%20of%20privacy%20is%20not%20compromised.%20Last%20week%2C%20a%20set%20of%20petitioners%20submitted%20guidelines%20for%20the%20seizure%20of%20devices%20which%20have%20been%20circulated%20to%20the%20government%20for%20possible%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell-known%20academics%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Madhava%20Prasad%2C%20Sujata%20Patel%2C%20Deepak%20Malghan%20and%20Mukul%20Kesavan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsupreme-court-circulates-interim-guidelines-for-seizure-of-devices%5C%22%3Epetitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202021%20to%20regulate%20the%20search%20of%20electronic%20devices%20by%20agents%20of%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20usually%20the%20police.%20In%20the%20course%20of%20hearings%2C%20these%20petitioners%20have%20suggested%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%2C%20to%20be%20issued%20as%20directions%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20hearing%20of%20another%20petition%20by%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Media%20Professionals%20last%20week%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20frame%20similar%20guidelines%20while%20observing%20that%20uncontrolled%20power%20to%20access%20devices%20of%20journalists%20was%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20hopefully%20come%20up%20with%20a%20substantive%20response%20to%20the%20circulated%20draft%20of%20guidelines%20in%20the%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%20case.%20The%20interim%20guidelines%20capture%20the%20due%20process%20followed%20in%20other%20mature%20democratic%20societies%2C%20and%20this%20should%20provide%20some%20guidance%20to%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Privacy%20Protection%20Act%20forbids%20any%20search%20or%20seizure%20of%20material%20belonging%20to%20those%20involved%20in%20First%20Amendment%20activities.%20Work%20related%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%20such%20as%20that%20of%20journalists%2C%20creative%20artists%2C%20academics%20and%20scientific%20researchers%20is%20protected%20by%20the%20First%20Amendment.%20Such%20materials%20are%20exempt%20from%20search%20as%20a%20source%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20forbids%20access%20to%20excluded%2C%20privileged%20or%20personal%20material%2C%20except%20under%20very%20stringent%20terms%2C%20and%20only%20if%20it%20is%20mandated%20by%20a%20judicial%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20laws%20of%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20USA%20have%20been%20placed%20before%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20a%20compilation%20submitted%20by%20the%20petitioner%20academics.%20Search%20without%20a%20judicial%20warrant%20is%20the%20exception%20rather%20than%20the%20rule%20in%20these%20countries%20but%20in%20India%2C%20it%20is%20just%20the%20opposite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20exactly%20is%20sought%20from%20an%20electronic%20device%2C%20and%20the%20reason%20for%20seeking%20it%20must%20be%20clearly%20stated%20in%20writing.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20no%20such%20system%20is%20followed%20by%20the%20Indian%20police%20or%20the%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%2090%20journalists%20connected%20with%20the%20online%20media%20platform%20NewsClick%2C%20the%20police%20arbitrarily%20took%20away%20some%20250%20devices%20(in%20some%20cases%2C%20three%20or%20more%20devices%20from%20a%20person)%20without%20following%20any%20of%20the%20procedures%20proposed%20in%20the%20interim%20guidelines%2C%20as%20they%20do%20not%20exist%20in%20the%20statutes%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20NewsClick%20case%20is%20still%20demanding%20to%20know%20the%20specific%20charge%20against%20him%2C%20which%20justifies%20imposing%20the%20draconian%20UAPA.%20It%20is%20not%20clearly%20stated%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20journalists%20whose%20devices%20have%20been%20seized%20are%20freelancers%20and%20have%20not%20been%20told%20what%20exactly%20the%20police%20seek%20from%20their%20devices.%20Their%20personal%20data%20and%20the%20work%20of%20a%20lifetime%20are%20now%20with%20the%20police.%20The%20NewsClick%20case%20also%20cries%20out%20for%20due%20process%20to%20be%20established%20for%20the%20seizure%20of%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20guidelines%20submitted%20by%20the%20petitioners%20in%20the%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%20case%2C%20the%20device%20seized%20must%20be%20first%20examined%20by%20an%20independent%20authority%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20owner%2Fagent%2C%20and%20all%20privileged%2C%20personal%20and%20professional%20material%20must%20be%20identified%2C%20separated%2C%20protected%20and%20returned%20immediately.%20Only%20material%20directly%20relevant%20to%20the%20investigation%20shall%20be%20taken%20away%20%E2%80%95%20after%20making%20three%20copies%2C%20one%20for%20the%20owner%2C%20one%20to%20be%20left%20sealed%20with%20the%20independent%20authority%20and%20the%20third%20taken%20for%20investigation%2C%20noting%20the%20hash%20value%20at%20every%20stage%20(which%20is%20used%20to%20validate%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20interim%20guidelines%20make%20the%20fundamental%20point%20that%20material%20illegally%20seized%20from%20electronic%20devices%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20used%20as%20evidence%20in%20any%20court%20of%20law.%20These%20ideas%20are%20fundamental%20for%20a%20civilised%20democracy%20which%20offers%20basic%20constitutional%20guarantees%20to%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20entirely%20reasonable%20to%20expect%20that%20something%20concrete%20should%20emerge%20from%20the%20interim%20guidelines%20suggested%20by%20senior%20advocate%20Nitya%20Ramakrishnan%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20petitioners%20in%20the%20Ram%20Ramaswamy%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mandatory%20legal%20requirement%20of%20a%20judicial%20warrant%20has%20arisen%20separately%20in%20cases%20relating%20to%20remotely%20accessing%20mobile%20phones%20via%20State-sponsored%20spyware%20attacks.%20Here%2C%20too%2C%20all%20the%20personal%20data%20on%20the%20device%20is%20illegally%20accessed%20and%20every%20activity%20of%20the%20phone%2C%20including%20remote%20access%20to%20the%20individual%E2%80%99s%20conversations%20even%20when%20the%20phone%20is%20not%20in%20use%2C%20gets%20tapped.%20Following%20the%20recent%20alert%20issued%20by%20Apple%20Inc%20to%20some%20Indian%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20journalists%20about%20possible%20%E2%80%9CState%20sponsored%E2%80%9D%20spyware%20attack%20on%20their%20iPhones%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3E(also%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Apple%20alert%3C%2Fa%3E)%20had%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20need%20for%20legal%20procedures%20such%20as%20a%20judicial%20order%20before%20accessing%20mobile%20phones%20of%20citizens.%20This%20issue%20had%20also%20come%20up%20during%20the%20Pegasus%20controversy%20when%20it%20was%20argued%20that%20the%20current%20laws%20don%E2%80%99t%20allow%20a%20spyware%20attack%20on%20mobile%20phones%2C%20exposing%20the%20entire%20data%20available%20in%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20sound%20legal%20provisions%2C%20whether%20for%20seizing%20devices%20or%20to%20remotely%20access%20devices%20using%20military%20spyware.%20Otherwise%2C%20privacy%20as%20a%20constitutional%20value%20would%20cease%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699931256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14083515%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-seizures-guidelines-rules-procedures%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20exactly%20is%20sought%20from%20an%20electronic%20device%2C%20and%20the%20reason%20for%20seeking%20it%20must%20be%20clearly%20stated%20in%20writing.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20no%20such%20system%20is%20followed%20by%20the%20Indian%20police%20or%20the%20agencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-seizures-guidelines-rules-procedures%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bareilly%3A%20Boy%2C%2018%2C%20caught%20trying%20to%20rape%204-yr-old%20girl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699931152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105202755%2Cimgsize-827152.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbareilly%2Fbareilly-boy-18-caught-trying-to-rape-4-yr-old-girl%2Farticleshow%2F105197682.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ASIF%20ANSARI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Umbrella%20Launches%20Brollie%2C%2