20continuing%20resolution%20is%20a%20necessary%20bill%20to%20place%20House%20Republicans%20in%20the%20best%20position%20to%20fight%20for%20conservative%20victories%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20will%20stop%20the%20absurd%20holiday-season%20omnibus%20tradition%20of%20massive%2C%20loaded%20up%20spending%20bills%20introduced%20right%20before%20the%20Christmas%20recess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20text%20of%20the%20legislation%20notably%20has%20some%20language%20that%20could%20work%20in%20the%20benefit%20of%20federal%20student-loan%20companies%20tasked%20with%20facilitating%20the%20return%20to%20repayment.%20In%20October%2C%20millions%20of%20federal%20borrowers%20once%20again%20started%20entering%20the%20repayment%20system%20after%20an%20over%20three-year%20pause%2C%20and%20the%20unprecedented%20transition%20has%20strained%20servicers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-bills-are-wrong-borrowers-servicers-fixing-errors-education-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleading%20them%20to%20make%20a%20range%20of%20errors%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20borrowers'%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson's%20proposal%20would%20give%20the%20Education%20Department%20flexibility%20to%20allocate%20more%20funding%20to%20the%20servicers%20to%20better%20support%20borrowers%20for%20purposes%20including%20student%20loan%20servicing%2C%20customer%20servicing%2C%20and%20other%20loan%20processing%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewould%20allow%20the%20department%20to%20reallocate%20other%20money%20in%20its%20budget%20toward%20loan%20servicing%2C%20and%20spend%20that%20money%20at%20a%20faster%20rate.%20The%20Education%20Department%20referred%20Insider%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20for%20a%20comment%20on%20the%20proposal.%20OMB%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Johnson's%20plan%20is%2