C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20employs%20a%20unique%20model%20which%20enables%20you%20to%20seamlessly%20transition%20between%20petrol%20and%20electric%20power%20within%20the%20same%20vehicle.%20To%20put%20it%20simply%2C%20the%20company%20converts%20your%20conventional%20petrol%20vehicle%20into%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20operate%20on%20both%20petrol%20and%20electric%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20your%20battery%20running%20out%20mid-journey%3B%20you%20can%20easily%20switch%20to%20petrol.%20As%20the%20founder%2C%20Ashish%20Dokania%2C%20aptly%20puts%20it%20for%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20having%20two%20scooters%20in%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20green%20mobility%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Ashish%20Donkaia%20had%20always%20been%20keen%20on%20building%20something%20on%20his%20own.%20Coming%20from%20a%20family%20of%20entrepreneurs%2C%20he%20says%20that%20the%20instincts%20were%20always%20there%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20who%20can%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0At%20the%20young%20age%20of%2021%2C%20Ashish%20started%20a%20business%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20young%20and%20naive%20and%20could%20not%20really%20sustain%20it.%20I%20decided%20to%20close%20it%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20While%20the%20business%20had%20to%20be%20closed%2C%20it%20ignited%20a%20spirit%20in%20Ashish%20to%20run%20a%20successful%20business%20one%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette