%20of%20raising%20Akshay%20was%20challenging.%20He%20felt%20depressed%2C%20he%20admits%2C%20thinking%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20him%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20will%20take%20care%20of%20him%20after%20us%3F%20This%20question%20plagues%20the%20mind%20of%20every%20parent%20of%20a%20disabled%20child.%20We%20have%20built%20this%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20that.%20I%20felt%20positive%20after%20building%20Sangopita.%20Akshay%20is%20also%20doing%20much%20better%20and%20has%20developed%20well%20in%20these%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20them%20wings%20to%20fly%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201498px)%20100vw%2C%201498px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%2062%20children%20in%20Sangopita%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529.jpeg%201498w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-300x176.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-500x293.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-768x450.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-150x88.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333895%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20are%2062%20children%20in%20Sangopita%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20children%20seem%20to%20have%20found%20their%20happy%20place%2C%20their%20parents%20describe%20Sangopita%20as%20a%20nurturing%20and%20thriving%20playground%20